  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Verify Stryker.NET availability: `dotnet tool install -g dotnet-stryker` (or local-tool variant). Capture version installed. If install fails, document and escalate.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Safety/` to enumerate the 13 files. Read `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Safety/` to see existing test coverage.</step>
    <step order="3">Create `stryker-config.json` (greenfield) targeting: source filter = `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Safety/*`; test project = `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/`. Configure mutators (default set is fine for pilot). Configure thresholds for reporting (NOT for failure — D-04 is measurement only).</step>
    <step order="4">Run Stryker: `dotnet stryker --config-file stryker-config.json`. Capture wall-clock time. If timeout/OOM, scope down to a single Safety subdirectory and document.</step>
    <step order="5">Parse Stryker HTML/JSON report to extract: overall mutation score; per-file scores; top-10 surviving mutants (by mutator type and assertion gap).</step>
    <step order="6">Author `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/mutation-testing-Services-Ai-Safety-2026-08-XX.md` with: executive summary; mutation score; top-10 surviving mutants table; r3 expansion recommendation; Stryker config record; tooling notes.</step>
    <step order="7">Verify `git status` shows ONLY: `stryker-config.json` (new); the new baseline doc. NO `src/` or test logic edits.</step>
    <step order="8">Commit message: "test(mutation): Stryker.NET pilot baseline for Services/Ai/Safety/* (FR-12)".</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Bash">install/run `dotnet-stryker`; parse output; `git status`; final commit</tool>
    <tool name="Read">enumerate Safety/ source + test files</tool>
    <tool name="Write">stryker-config.json (new); baseline report doc (new)</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="config">stryker-config.json (new; greenfield Stryker.NET configuration)</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/baseline/mutation-testing-Services-Ai-Safety-2026-08-XX.md</output>
  </outputs>

